title: Manchester United total revenue 2009 to 2019
summary: In general Revenue in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Revenue in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2011 to 2012, gradually increasing from 2012 to 2016, and finally roughly constant from 2016 to 2019.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2015 and 2016.
Maximum Revenue in million U.S. dollars, about 796.4 was reported at Year 2019
Minimum Revenue in million U.S. dollars about 421.27 was reached at Year 2012
